    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should ask my doctor but they're super hard to get a hold of and i'm just so exhausted right now. i feel like i'm gonna crash during work tomorrow if i don't get some sleep tonight. like, melatonin is just a natural supplement and zolpidem is the medicine, so shouldn't they just work together to help me drift off? it doesn't seem that dangerous if i'm just trying to sleep.",
